data.description: The Hunt Club- beautifully updated, well-maintained End of Group Stone Front Townhouse with lots of amenities and privacy of a single-family home! This 3BR, 2.5BA end-unit, with a finished lower level and 2-car garage, offers over 2000+ sq ft of living space and many windows for natural light. The location is probably one of the best in the community because it is located at the end of the street, with no other units behind it, allowing for incomparable views, privacy, and extra parking. The home features:  a large eat-in kitchen,  New Granite countertops/ Back Splash, a Farmhouse Sink, and New Lighting throughout,   with a slider overlooking a Newer Deck,  where you are sure to spend many relaxing hours. Freshly painted.  A Primary suite features a walk-in closet and whirlpool bath. The lower level has a finished family room, storage, and access to the 2-car garage.  The seller will consider all reasonable offers.  There is also space to park in the driveway and an "overflow" parking lot in the community. Super convenient to I83,  for the MD commuter, and tons of shopping, restaurants, and conveniences. Don't miss the opportunity to own this rare find.
